Best Practices
	1.	Maintain Clear Grok Patterns  
   Use explicit patterns to reduce ambiguity in parsing.

	1.	Implement Comprehensive Logging  
   Always log unmatched lines and reasons for failures.

	1.	Iterative Improvement  
   Regularly update auto_correct_line to handle recurring log quirks.

	1.	Batch Test Before Deployment  
   Test patterns against a variety of sample log files before production use.

	1.	Monitor and Adapt  
   Regularly review grok_parsing.log to identify trends and potential optimizations.

